{"tid":1263294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港國歌】商台聽眾合唱團 - 香港之歌 (1969)","createTime":"2019-06-28T06:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T16:13:29.000Z","uid":35221,"like":79,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"09479fdaf3b6f6edf34dd7ac65b63c64d59f3404","tid":1263294,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qf-hFthH65A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQf-hFthH65A&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=3f9d047f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qf-hFthH65A</a><br />\n<br />\n香港之歌 (1969)<br />\n主唱：商台聽眾合唱團 <br />\n作曲：鄺天培<br />\n填詞：鄒方里 <br />\n<br />\n維多利亞海港，爐峰輕眺盡遠望， <br />\n萬千氣象，樂滿華堂，繁盛自由更安康。 <br />\n<br />\n維多利亞海港，民主可貴得眾望， <br />\n外銷工業遐邇名揚，無限貿易流暢。 <br />\n<br />\n處處景致秀麗，大眾喜氣洋洋， <br />\n和平共處，名聞四方，讚賞東方之珠香港。 <br />\n<br />\n維多利亞海港，民風謙遜重禮讓， <br />\n共享歡樂，大眾安康，愛東方之珠香港。 <br />\n<br />\n南北中西安逸歡暢，同聲頌讚香港， <br />\n勁秀好山城，地老天長，民主之光照香港。 <br />\n<br />\n名昌千秋，聲譽不降，同舟共濟永自強， <br />\n美滿又安寧，是個好天堂，成就是大眾共創。 <br />\n<br />\n維多利亞海港，爐峰輕眺盡遠望， <br />\n萬千氣象，樂滿華堂，繁盛自由更安康。 <br />\n<br />\n維多利亞海港，民主可貴得眾望， <br />\n外銷工業遐邇名揚，無限貿易流暢。 <br />\n<br />\n處處景致秀麗，大眾喜氣洋洋， <br />\n和平共處，名聞四方，讚賞東方之珠香港。 <br />\n<br />\n維多利亞海港，民風謙遜重禮讓， <br />\n共享歡樂，大眾安康，愛東方之珠香港。"},{"pid":"7c8e58dfe07f0480937f6f13a117bab994ab1ec3","tid":1263294,"uid":51720,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"其實係響應「香港節」而創作嘅歌曲之一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7467837228b2a2a80f9ddead8cf94f2f4d884e","tid":1263294,"uid":35221,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"7c8e58dfe07f0480937f6f13a117bab994ab1ec3","tid":1263294,"uid":51720,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"其實係響應「香港節」而創作嘅歌曲之一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1969年，六七暴動平息冇耐，港英搞咗個香港節穩定民心、粉飾太平，嘗試提升返香港人對香港嘅歸屬感。商業電台六七暴動都元氣大傷，尤其播音員林彬(六七暴動期間林彬參演廣播劇《欲罷不能》、《大丈夫日記》，日日公開直屌匪。《欲罷不能》同之後另一個廣播劇節目《冷眼旁觀》就係《十八樓C座》前身)畀匪害死。香港之歌就係當年其中一首響應香港節嘅歌。1971年同1973年再搞過兩次，不過當時社會氣氛已經平靜曬，唔同69年，之後都冇再搞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.seewide.com/upload/article/201603/1456832178382104091.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.seewide.com%2Fupload%2Farticle%2F201603%2F1456832178382104091.jpg&h=2df92cc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/81/1e/86/811e86aefc25ea75467850ff0112364c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F81%2F1e%2F86%2F811e86aefc25ea75467850ff0112364c.jpg&h=078a191b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.wetoasthk.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/1969%E5%B9%B4%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%B1%86%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AF%80%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%A3%9D%E9%A3%BE-%E6%85%B6%E7%A5%9D%E7%89%8C%E6%A8%93.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F1969%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B1%2586%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25AF%2580%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25A3%259D%25E9%25A3%25BE-%25E6%2585%25B6%25E7%25A5%259D%25E7%2589%258C%25E6%25A8%2593.png&h=5b4e061e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkstmp.com/fd691209.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkstmp.com%2Ffd691209.JPG&h=46bae8d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkstmp.com/oldfoto05.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkstmp.com%2Foldfoto05.JPG&h=e5ef4d2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://gaahk.org.hk/wp-content/uploads/cover-b-225x300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaahk.org.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fcover-b-225x300.jpg&h=12f59e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.grs.gov.hk/ws/online/GPM/filemanager/template/common/images/festival_of_hong_kong/po000095.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.grs.gov.hk%2Fws%2Fonline%2FGPM%2Ffilemanager%2Ftemplate%2Fcommon%2Fimages%2Ffestival_of_hong_kong%2Fpo000095.jpg&h=9a135d13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a79398c4295b5e7b6a240acb6c5d36fd9d48c451","tid":1263294,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:17:43.000Z","msg":"作曲鄺天培係商業電台開台初期營業部經理、中文節目部主任。除咗做幕後，亦都有參演過廣播劇同作過曲。作品有莫佩雯(秦煌老婆)〈勁草嬌花〉、尹芳玲〈薔薇之戀〉(1961年商台長篇廣播劇薔薇之戀主題曲)。連埋〈香港之歌〉，呢幾首歌都收入慶祝商業電台啟播十周年嘅《商台歌集第一輯》(1969)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ww3.sinaimg.cn/large/68f631fajw1eppc034hqgj20g80dsgnp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww3.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F68f631fajw1eppc034hqgj20g80dsgnp.jpg&h=63e5284f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"022390d4a6523d669635f52cc2007203659d6bc6","tid":1263294,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2adadc95c9adb1feed35f65b8b60bd4478f952","tid":1263294,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cb9ee969b8401d81c8813ec5515e4621b86ac9","tid":1263294,"uid":119277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:54:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9e5eeacc52726afe78b2cc53bd458dd5b0116fb","tid":1263294,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e187694d569c35ab024db4ae2f82f3a8992a154","tid":1263294,"uid":247082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:5